I am happy to adjust the cap if rollback miraculously appears between now and October and the demand is there. Otherwise, I am trying to make sure I can deliver a quality event with my level of experience with running online tournaments (low versus in-person brackets).",,"East Coast, Southeast, Midwest, Atlantic Canada allowed
Anything else REQUIRES connection test before going forward",,"None known at this time. Degica (pre-Komodo HI rebrand) has helped in the past, but we haven't gotten that from them this year.",,"None, at 32 cap it doesn't change significantly.",,,
