rnaments/121222,,,"Fri. 10/11, Fri. 10/18, Fri. 11/01, Fri. 11/08, Sat. 10/12, Sun. 10/13",,To add to the winner must keep character/team rule. The winner is allowed to change their teams order if their opponent switches teams.,,,Thank you for the opportunity to host Skullgirls for Vortex Gallery. We look forward to the event and hope it runs well. Here's to 10 more years of Skullgirls!,,"US, Canada and Mexico",,I'll look into this but I prefer all payouts be put into a matcherino.,,"I run pot split amounts from Matcherino amount thresholds. Lowest placing person will at least get $10. Here are my following splits:
Top 3 - $75
Top 4 - $150
Top 6 - $320
Top 8 - $660

I run my own calculations on an excel doc provided by the House of 3000.
",I'll also look into this with the developers. We can get codes for the game and relics for Skullgirls Mobile players.,,
